Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:36.15,Title Part 5,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(402,394)\pos(107,923)\fs60}Episodio 26  A Little Story From the Past ~My Name Is Doppio~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.87,0:01:36.40,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is a little story from the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:41.37,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It all began during the summer of 1965.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.95,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Prisoner 696! \NWhat's the matter with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:48.08,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Prisoner 696!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.59,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Did you eat something spoiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.97,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,She's pregnant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:57.84,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,This is a women's prison on a remote island.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:01.10,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,The inmates and guards are all women!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:02.93,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Not to mention this prisoner...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.93,0:02:05.73,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,...was sentenced to ten years \Nfor bank robbery and assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:08.39,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,She's been doing time here for two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.39,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,{\an8}Push! Just a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.65,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,When could she have become pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:13.07,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,She didn't look this far along earlier today{I feel iit's important that we get across that she's saying she didn't look pregnant earlier THIS SAME DAY. -Starfish}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.21,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.49,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Hey, prisoner! \NJust who exactly is this kid's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.87,Flashback,Diavolo's Mom,0,0,0,,He's... dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.86,Flashback,Diavolo's Mom,0,0,0,,For more than... two years now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.54,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,That's bullshit! {But I believe it. -Giorno Giovanna}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:34.15,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,You'd have an easier time convincing me\Nyou grew a barnacle in your knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:45.72,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Looks like the baby made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.39,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Yes... But something's not right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:51.19,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,His eyes have been open \Nsince the moment he was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:54.73,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,And he isn't crying at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:02.16,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,This should go without saying, \Nbut we can't raise a child here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.91,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,We'll find him a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.81,Flashback,Lady,0,0,0,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:11.53,Flashback,Diavolo's Mom,0,0,0,,Sar...di...nia...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:25.64,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,A priest from a small village \Non the island took the baby in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:33.44,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,{\an8}Time passed in the blink of an eye, and the boy gained a reputation for being cowardly and a bit slow as he grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:37.28,Flashback,Doppio,0,0,0,,Well, I gotta get going.\N Bye bye, Mr. Froggy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.55,Flashback,Man,0,0,0,,Hey, watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:42.82,Flashback,Man,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:44.62,Flashback,Man,0,0,0,,Stay closer to the side, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.74,Flashback,Man,0,0,0,,And don't tell the priest about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:48.95,Flashback,Doppio,0,0,0,,Th-That was a close one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:52.67,Flashback,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you weren't squished.{He's talking about the frog, not himself. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:54.17,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,Do you like frogs?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.34,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,I like them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.88,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,I don't like bugs, though. {Didn't really like this without a subject... :D}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:04:00.22,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,Or guys who stink, for that matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:06.60,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,I don't like anything that isn't pretty.{She's not saying "I dislike bugs, stinky guys and ugly things", but "I dislike ugly things, among which are bugs and stinky guys." -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:09.81,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,You from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.06,Flashback,Doppio,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... {Toni, should there be something before "Y-Yeah"? -G}{Nah -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.05,Flashback,Doppio,0,0,0,,It's kinda hot, \Nso would you like to get a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.55,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.28,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,...I will, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:26.20,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,I feel like sparkling water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:28.87,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,Hard water from France.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.50,Flashback,Donatella,0,0,0,,Your treat, I hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.54,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,You'd like to become a sailor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:36.71,Flashback,Doppio,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.21,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.34,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,You're certainly a simple man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.22,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,That sounds like a perfect fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:53.52,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:57.69,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,He walked all this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.57,Flashback,Guy,0,0,0,,Good for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.82,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should buy him a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:05.86,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,In order to build a garage next to his room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.70,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...the priest began digging into the floor with a pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.37,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.92,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,A dead body?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.55,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,No, it's too...{It's literally like "No, for it to be that it's...", probably implying something about the body being way too well preserved for being a long-since buried corpse. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:27.26,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,After carefully picking away the surrounding concrete...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.93,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,...he found a woman underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.22,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It was the woman who gave birth \Nto the boy the priest took in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.69,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,Sh-She's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:42.90,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,She was incapable of moving or talking,\N but somehow she was kept alive{"...through unknown means." Maybe not essential information, but it is part of the JP. -Starfish}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:45.40,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,How many years had it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:48.49,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,The woman had lost all sense of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:51.28,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Hatred? Love?{Okay, this is oddly phrased in general. I *THINK* it's trying to say that, like, her heart was shrouded in darkness so nobody could tell what sort of emotions she held in there. Even the manga doesn't provide any additional context to this quote. What's in the anime here is word for word what he said about it in the manga. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.37,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,All that remained in her heart was darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.77,Flashback,Priest,0,0,0,,This hair color...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:10.85,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,That night, a great fire and strong winds\Nled to every house in the village burning down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:15.77,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,It's unknown what caused it. \NSeven people died, and several others went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:22.33,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,On the list of the deceased were the names of the priest and the boy he had taken in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:38.96,Main,Boy,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:42.54,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:45.13,Main,Boy,0,0,0,,I know, you pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:46.51,Main,Boy,0,0,0,,There's a truck coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.14,Main,Driver,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:56.02,Main,Driver,0,0,0,,Where the hell do you think you're going, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:03.11,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,O-Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.69,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Aww... Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:07.99,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Misjudged that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.16,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You appear down on your luck. \NHaving a rough day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:18.20,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Or perhaps you've been \Nexperiencing misfortune for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.71,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Sounds about right. \NI've had nonstop problem after{ another.}{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.47,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,How about I tell you your fortune?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.05,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I'll make it cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.10,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Huh? Nah, I'll pass...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:37.35,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You call Sardinia your home, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:42.98,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,It's been quite some time \Nsince you were last here, hasn't it? {They're IN Sardinia}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.69,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'd hardly call that fortunetelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:50.03,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,One look is all you need \Nto tell that I'm a traveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.95,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Anyone could figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.95,0:07:55.99,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You're... living with a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.54,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Light and shadow, exposed and concealed.{The latter part is literally "front and back", referring to something that's out in the open for anyone to see, and something else that's hidden. I'm kinda considering "Something revealed and something concealed", but I'm not sure if that ACTUALLY sounds poetic or if it just sounds dumb. Your call. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:02.25,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You may see it as leading two separate lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:07.88,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,But due to your unyielding personality and \N willingness to use your dark secret to your advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:11.13,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,...you have enjoyed an endless streak of victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.59,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.68,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Oh, please forgive my rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:21.18,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You possess a quality that would compel \Nany fortune teller to want to tell you your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:24.23,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Please, allow me to do it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:27.15,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I'll make it 20,000... no, 10,000 lire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:30.99,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Everyone has at least a few little secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.20,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Aren't you just saying things that could apply to anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.37,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You're looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:38.66,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You're currently looking for \Nsomeone very important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.79,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Everyone spends their lives looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:47.25,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,A beautiful girlfriend or a good friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.25,0:08:51.09,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,But I have to admit it feels good\N for someone to read me so well.{Literally "It feels nice to have things that are on point said about me." -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.88,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,How do you tell fortunes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:54.22,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,With that crystal ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.64,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,No... I began telling your fortune much earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:01.39,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I could tell simply by the shape \Nof the mud stain on your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:05.69,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,It's been said for thousands of years \Nthat in Romani fortunetelling... {http://rozvitok.org/en/fortune-telling-as-part-of-the-roma-culture/}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:10.11,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,...the strongest conclusions are derived by studying shapes formed by chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:13.07,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,That is the symbol of your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.95,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Your daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.03,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.58,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,The person you seek is your very own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:25.50,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You returned to Sardinia to find the child\N of the woman you left fifteen years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:26.21,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.25,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Huh?\N No... That can't be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.00,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,You're rather young...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:34.09,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I know what I just said, but this is very odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:37.72,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Whose child? Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:37.72,Secondary,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,But you have one. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.47,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Let me see your palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.02,0:09:40.91,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.47,0:09:43.52,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Please! \NMy pride as a fortuneteller is at stake here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.73,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let go of my hand... Don't touch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.73,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I won't make you pay!\N In fact, I'll pay {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.56,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,20,000... No, I'll pay you 100,000 lire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:50.57,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:54.94,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You're getting on my nerves! \NHands off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:57.53,Main,Doppio & Diavolo,0,0,0,,What good will it do for you, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.74,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Especially now that I'm going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:08.43,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your face... Your age...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:10.46,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You... do not seem to be a Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:16.80,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You built your business with the wisdom to see people for who they truly are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.68,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Nothing could have brought you greater misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:26.89,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Those who know even a hint of my true nature cannot be allowed to exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:32.07,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Though you've demonstrated to me\N that you are a skilled fortuneteller.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:38.03,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I will respect that skill by giving you \Na quick and painless death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.87,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,But I must ask you something first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.87,0:10:43.16,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,This man is named Risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:44.58,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,He has betrayed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:50.29,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,He's searching for my daughter\N in order to uncover my true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.84,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Tell me where he is at this exact moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.92,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.26,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I can't tell that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:01.14,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,But I'm certain you'll soon encounter him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:04.01,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,He's here in Sardinia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:08.35,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,His heart is filled with vengeance, \Nand you will certainly encounter him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:11.60,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I see. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.44,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,That will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:18.44,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I knew it! I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.53,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Light and shadow, exposed and concealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.12,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Two personalities!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:26.08,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,So long as you hold onto this secret, \Nthe death of others will bring with it good fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.33,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,...and you will bask in eternal splendor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:32.21,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,What a beautiful palm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:34.59,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I've never seen a hand like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:38.84,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,Huh? This isn't right. \NIt looks strange, somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.97,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,The lifeline has completely changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:43.79,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:49.56,Main,Fortune Teller,0,0,0,,This is my own hand! \NIt changed before I even realized it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.34,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,King Crimson.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:09.08,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.71,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you weren't squished!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:15.88,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Crawling around on the sidewalk is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:17.34,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Go on, shoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:19.47,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Be careful. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.37,0:12:26.41,Main,Boy,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.81,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,Where to, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.27,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Costa Smeralda, please. {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Costa_Smeralda}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.02,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.65,0:12:41.61,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now onto our next story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:46.41,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,{\an8}We'll be investigating the site of \Nthe crash off the Olbia Coast in Sardinia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.83,Main,Lady,0,0,0,,{\an8}However...
Comment: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,B {Edited up to here -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.71,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Mr. Driver, do you have a phone \NI can use to call someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:01.92,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Mine is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.01,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,Sorry, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.30,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.97,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,C-Could you stop for one second, Mr. Driver?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.39,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'll get out here! \NThis is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.93,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm fine getting out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:14.26,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,That's the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.40,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:21.40,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I just need to keep watch over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.28,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,Sardinia, Costa Smeralda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.28,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,,For a time, this area was forgotten by history... {Had to remove "until about 50 years ago" since it made transitioning into the next line extremely awkward -J}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:36.92,Narrator,Narrator,0,0,0,, ...until a millionaire from India became enamored with the sight of the winds meeting the cliffs off the coast and decided to call it his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.13,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.91,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,There seems to be an extra digit on your meter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:46.13,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,{\an8}You trying to say I'm ripping you off\N by rigging the meter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.97,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,You really think I'd do that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:52.31,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,N-No... But 800,000 lire to go \Nfrom the city to here seems a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.31,0:13:53.81,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...I just can't afford it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:56.44,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,Like hell a tourist can't afford it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:59.40,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,I know you hid something\N in your pocket earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:04.99,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,You hid an envelope in your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.20,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:08.08,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on, cough it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:10.41,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Don't touch me... I-I'm getting a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.99,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,See? I knew it! {The alternating thickness in the outline of Doppio's hair line is bothering me -Gyro}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.92,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:23.34,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Those who bear witness to that which should remain unseen \Ncannot be allowed to continue existing in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.95,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,Y-You fucking...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.08,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.97,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hey... Did you hear that phone ringing just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:34.64,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.18,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Where did it come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:38.90,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hey! I asked you a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.90,0:14:42.02,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,That phone is too busted up to have been ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.61,Main,Taxi,0,0,0,,H-Hell if I know! \NWhat are you{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.74,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring! \NRing ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.11,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,There it is again! \NWhere is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.41,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.49,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:55.16,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:59.62,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hey, why didn't you say something? \NYou have a car phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.63,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:05.17,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hello?\N Yes, this is Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:08.68,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Boss! \NYes, I just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.93,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,It's the place from the photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.97,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I just need to keep watch here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:21.35,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't need to eliminate the driver \Nsince he didn't see what was in the envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.31,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,If I may interject, Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:27.32,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...I'm fairly sure he saw the photo \Nyou told me not to show to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:30.45,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,R-Right. I apologize, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.49,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm about to start watching the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.49,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You're about to start watching the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.70,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,No, my Doppio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:42.46,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Slowly, but surely, look to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.59,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Don't make any sudden moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.17,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,The only thing being watched right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.80,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...is you, Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:52.76,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Th-That's... Risotto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.80,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,The traitorous hitman!{I figure since his group was called the "Hitman Team", we should probably use "Hitman" rather than "Assassin" to describe him. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.43,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,He appeared just like the fortuneteller said!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.73,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Apparently, because of the plane crash...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:04.40,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...he learned of the existence of \Nthe photo at Trish's house in Sardinia. {HOW?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.53,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,He must be eliminated first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:10.61,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Otherwise, he'll interfere when Trish arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.99,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I will be the one to finish him off...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:19.16,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,...but you must get close to him \Nwithout revealing who you are.{CR had "without him realizing my identity", but he clearly says "OMAE no shoutai", which is "YOUR identity"... I mean, since they're both the same guy I suppose technically either works, but... -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:22.87,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Risotto's ability is a mystery to me, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:25.67,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Drag him out so that he gets\N within two meters of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.84,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,At that range, King Crimson will surely eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.63,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:33.51,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I'm hanging up, my Doppio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.85,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:36.55,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Click!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.39,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.39,0:16:42.69,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,My head... really hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:45.73,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,O-Oh, yeah. \NNow isn't the time to worry about a headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.73,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I just finished talking to the boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:52.74,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,My mission is to keep an eye on that building and... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.49,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.16,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Get closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.16,0:16:57.99,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Right!\N I have to get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.87,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,But to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.87,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I won't go anywhere near you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:12.30,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Look this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.64,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.35,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,I... feel like I've seen him before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.35,0:17:19.43,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,Wh-Who is he again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:20.85,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Move your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.93,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I can't see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.85,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I-I don't have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.78,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:35.53,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Why does this always happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:36.99,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I must have imagined it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:41.20,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,The ignorance and fear in his expression aren't an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.54,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,He wouldn't be acting like this if he were from Passione.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:47.71,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Not to mention, he's more unguarded than a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.72,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,He must be a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:53.85,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:56.05,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Quit screaming. \NI'm just picking up my knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.01,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I don't care about you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:04.56,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I-I don't feel so good...\N{Oh my god he's been Thanos'd! What an underwhelming way for the main villain of this Part to go. -Starfish} My head hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:08.52,Thoughts,Doppio,0,0,0,,T-Two meters...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.90,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:14.44,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,There was one thing you did\N that seemed like an act...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:17.24,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,When you fell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:20.38,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...you reflexively hid the envelope \Nso I wouldn't see it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:24.75,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It's right under your left shoe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.96,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,What are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.92,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I'll leave if I'm satisfied with what I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:31.00,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:34.51,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I-I don't have any money!\N Just let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:40.26,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I didn't sense any murderous intent or hostility, but your expression just now seemed faked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.97,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Stand up, move your left leg, and show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.39,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I told you to stand up! \NStand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:53.57,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just an envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.90,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Looks like it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.78,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Your trembling certainly isn't an act...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:03.08,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...and I can tell you're a coward who's incapable of lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:08.58,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,But now... I'm even more interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.71,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You're definitely a Stand user.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.55,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You heard that sound, too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:18.72,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Just now, you glanced at the source of the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.43,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,That's the sound of scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:24.31,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Something is scouting this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:26.49,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,That sound and shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.85,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,...is Aerosmith!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.10,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,They're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:36.86,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,And who are you to show up \Nto such an important location?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:40.11,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,It must mean the boss \Nhas complete trust in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:44.03,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,But at the same time, \Nyou clearly have true fear in your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.03,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,You're a walking contradiction!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.37,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.63,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,You're the one who's about to be shaking in your boots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:53.79,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:57.17,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Since you're running at me, \Nyou must be a close-ranged power type.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.38,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,Your range is about two or three meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.34,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,As long as I know that, I can kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:07.35,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,What... the... M-My throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.51,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Th-These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:14.27,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,...actual razor blades?!{I am genuinely amazed that this isn't censored. -Starfish}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:21.11,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,T-Two meters, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.57,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I'll take these razor blades \Nand shove them right up your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:26.78,Main,Risotto,0,0,0,,I just said I know how to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:34.79,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Impossible!\N I'm not done yet, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.17,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,H-He disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.89,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,That's his... \NThat's his hitman ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:46.22,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,But how...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:48.45,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.81,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:54.90,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I can hear a phone ringing somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.11,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Brrring ring ring ring ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:59.78,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:02.74,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,By complete coincidence,\N there happens to be a payphone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:03.61,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Click!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.11,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Beep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:05.95,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:07.87,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,My Doppio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.41,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Wh-Where are you, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:12.33,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Are you nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.00,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Please come quickly if you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.42,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:20.46,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,I am unable to join you \Nuntil you get close enough to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:26.18,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,This will all be for naught\N if he's able to see me and escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:27.22,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:31.02,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,You must get closer! \NYou need to be within two meters of Risotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:34.64,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,Boss! \NI don't know what his ability is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:36.48,Main,Doppio,0,0,0,,He could attack me again at any second!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:38.31,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Doppio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.44,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Oh, Doppio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.44,0:21:43.28,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,My precious Doppio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:48.87,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Have you already forgotten that I gave you a portion of my King Crimson's ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.75,Main,Diavolo,0,0,0,,Now is the time to use it!
